{"tid":1040193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男遭綁架餵吃硬硬藥　逼跟男啪啪啪23小時","createTime":"2019-02-28T02:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T15:09:47.000Z","uid":121473,"like":193,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"74da7df1cda6b0451e02d5782797aa6538dcb5de","tid":1040193,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:14:39.000Z","msg":"南非一名50歲男子被綁架後，綁匪逼他吃藥讓下體硬硬，要他跟另一男子連續23小時啪啪啪。<br />\n<br />\n據《dailysun》報導，南非約翰尼斯堡一名50歲男子受到了創傷，因為他被迫連續23小時啪啪啪，他指出從沒想過會被綁架，被帶到帕克通尼安普羅提(Braamfontein)的一間房子內。男子說被綁架時他被纏上眼罩，當貨車載他到目的地，「當她們拿下眼罩後，發現我被帶到一間臥室，裡面有一個講塞索托語(Sesotho)的女人，和一個穿著紅色短褲的印度男子」。<br />\n<br />\n男子說，綁匪給他了一顆藥丸讓他下體保持硬硬，並且強迫他跟印度男子啪啪啪，女子則是在旁拍攝雙方的激戰過程，「她們第二天早上才讓我離開」。警方發言人姆貝利（Xoli Mbele）指出，該起綁架性侵案已經在調查。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190228/1525028/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190228%2F1525028%2F&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7TdxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=31edb659\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190228%2F1525028%2F&h=279e7b9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190228/1525028/</a>"},{"pid":"8315ed30191d50de0f24d52847f1684bee430f6a","tid":1040193,"uid":17628,"like":322,"dislike":6,"score":316,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:16:31.000Z","msg":"俾人綁架仲有得屌人仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n慘過死"},{"pid":"111dfcd377397c13e68a4563e2c563bd38a990ca","tid":1040193,"uid":162539,"like":394,"dislike":5,"score":389,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media0.giphy.com/media/B1wcqcc4zEUvK/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia0.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FB1wcqcc4zEUvK%2Fgiphy.gif&h=e29eda25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6bfa7f688c744d89e2075e8c29f25ccc0c03bde","tid":1040193,"uid":84869,